Text: Two DocumentsRecently I have come into possession of copies of two partially executed documents between our companies and I have been asked by my boss to follow up to procure one original of our Electronic Trading Agreement and one copy of our fully executed Password Application On January our counsel Elaine M Walsh both faxed and FedExd three items to youan EnronOnline Electronic Trading Agreement Password Application and Customer Registration Form Again if you would be so kind as to forward one of the originals of the Trading Agreement and one copy of the Password Application I would greatly appreciate it If you have in fact already returned an original to us way back when I would be grateful to receive a copy of this fully executed document Very many thanks Sincerely Elise M Devlin Administrative Assistant Edison Mission Marketing Trading Inc
